<doc id="326724" wikidata="Q99943110" url="?curid=326724" title="Broadway Records">
<text>Broadway Records has been the name of three otherwise unrelated American record labels:

* Broadway Records (1920s), founded in the early 1920s in Bridgeport, Connecticut
* Broadway Records (1947), founded in 1947 in Los Angeles
* Broadway Records (2012), founded in 2012</text><links>
